Grandium Responsive WordPress Hotel Theme

The modern design and strong typography makes Grandium the perfect WordPress Hotel Theme for any hotel / motel / appointment / spa website. Grandium sections/parts that come together with the theme are compatible with WordPress shortcode and Visual Composer structure. Therefore, we can promise that you will not come across with any surprises while building any page that you imagine. All pages of the template are built with the shortcodes which include hundreds of properties and you can easily build as many different pages as you like. We have added Booking Appointment, which is a very strong and flexible plugin, so that you can make appointment with your customers, you will not need to pay 49$ because it is integrated into the theme. Grandium uses this extension for hotel room booking and you will have to purchase a license to use this extension HBook – Hotel booking system – WordPress Plugin Paid plugin Do not you have coding knowledge? Do not worry because you will not need to use even a line of code, build your pages by dragging and dropping via the Visual Composer page builder and theme options. As you can apply your favorite colors to the general design of theme with a single click, you can also use the colors and images that you like with the options in Visual Composer shortcodes.
